overview: Susuk is a 2008 Malaysian horror film which was released on August 7, 2008 in Malaysia. The film is directed by Amir Muhammad and Naeim Ghalili. The story concerns about Soraya, who uses the forbidden practice of susuk in order to be famous.
tagline: Don't Let It Eat Yourself [Jangan Sampai Makan Diri]
title: Susuk
